        "subject": "LU-11300 lnet: simplify lnet_handle_local_failure()",
        "message": "LU-11300 lnet: simplify lnet_handle_local_failure()\n\nPass the struct lnet_ni to lnet_handle_local_failure() instead of the\nmessage structure, since nothing else from the message is being\nused. This also makes symmetrical with lnet_handle_remote_failure()\n\nLustre-change: https://review.whamcloud.com/33452\nLustre-commit: f8c7dd6f53748cf589b2a1f18d93b92761f9d983\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <ashehata@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Olaf Faaland <faaland1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I7a96607e3feb66d3abe5fffc0bbf10fa919afc10\n"
